         <abstract id="aspace_0f89c4a9df99b08be99bd27c1487ce85">The records consist of 16mm films and a videotape produced by the Yale Office of Development. Included are "Tradition of Leadership," "Yale: 275th Year," and "Why Yale Needs All that Money."</abstract>
